cat << EOF
pekwm is a windowmanager based on aewm++ but it no longer resembles it. 
It is highly configurable and rather fast. One can group windows in a 
sense much like pwm. Keybindings, Rootmenu, Mouse button actions and 
Automatic properties are configurable. 
EOF
